titles.title: A bill to extend and modify the temporary suspension of duty on (R,S)--2-((2,6-dimethylphenyl)methoxyacetylamino) propionic acid, methyl ester.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 5/7/2012--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to provide temporarily for the duty treatment of (R,S)-2-((2,6-dimethylphenyl)methoxyacetylamino) propionic acid, methyl ester.
